collectors.titleDetails: (2 total Queries, 2 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql:
select *,ee.name as sumber_data from urusan as aa
		inner join sub_urusan as bb on aa.id=bb.id_urusan
		inner join ikk as cc on bb.id=cc.id_sub_urusan
		inner join rumus as dd on cc.id=dd.id_ikk
		inner join sy_category as ee on dd.sumber_data=ee.id
		where aa.output_outcome='OP'
		order by aa.id asc, bb.id asc, cc.id asc, dd.id

timelineData.name: Query
timelineData.query:
select *,ee.name as sumber_data from urusan as aa
		inner join sub_urusan as bb on aa.id=bb.id_urusan
		inner join ikk as cc on bb.id=cc.id_sub_urusan
		inner join rumus as dd on cc.id=dd.id_ikk
		inner join sy_category as ee on dd.sumber_data=ee.id
		where aa.output_outcome='OP'
		order by aa.id asc, bb.id asc, cc.id asc, dd.id
